{"tid":2155760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中學校長會主席鄧振強退休前專訪：教自由民主是教育初心 籲教師秉持專業勿畏縮","createTime":"2020-08-14T04:08:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T14:42:11.000Z","uid":36494,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"848918985c412df4b291562b6a96a72c82d57c98","tid":2155760,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:08:11.000Z","msg":"香港經歷了最動盪的一年，有社會賢達更揚言「放棄年輕人」，中學校長會主席鄧振強當時反而呼籲年輕人「不要放棄香港，不要放棄希望」。這位敢言校長本月底退休前接受《蘋果》專訪，強調教導學生為自由和民主努力，是教育初心，也是政府官方文件列明的教育目標，他作為校長，一直「好乖」和「跟規矩」執行此項政府政策。對於教育界近年屢成政治風眼，鄧校長慨嘆：「將來嘅日子，自由同埋民主，會唔會變成敏感詞呢？係唔講得呢喺學校？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200814/RHHCYFVK75FFTIJXLWIXRRESD4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200814%2FRHHCYFVK75FFTIJXLWIXRRESD4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBRyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=b9dc3d73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200814%2FRHHCYFVK75FFTIJXLWIXRRESD4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=201036ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200814/RHHCYFVK75FFTIJXLWIXRRESD4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"9c8f7a02718d577c3f1a61f18c273e07d024171c","tid":2155760,"uid":36494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:09:48.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">2000年教改，教育統籌委員會提交《香港教育制度改革建議》，列明21世紀的教育目標，包括讓每個人「願意為社會的繁榮、進步、自由和民主不斷努力，為國家和世界的前途作出貢獻。」</span></span>鄧校長說，不少人大概已將這份報告當成「歷史文件」，忘掉了教育的初心，但學界一直堅持這教育目標，若說自由和民主是這代學生的核心價值，也的確是學校培養出來。"},{"pid":"4e321807056a0fcba3442bb4db2089ef92a37cbf","tid":2155760,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:10:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"45f360a52064219bb34d754c9bb57dd9a743155c","tid":2155760,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:10:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ccda66afd80bcefd76bf96a733653eeb5965375c","tid":2155760,"uid":128014,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:11:05.000Z","msg":"點解個名差一個字，人品就差咁遠嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20d94cd7bc9f57f9cfecc003e8ca1062515267b8","tid":2155760,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:14:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"853923a4b655969acd5d34b3837e8c679e3dfec5","tid":2155760,"uid":32859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:27:27.000Z","msg":"睇到鄧同強就覺得係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2bb74f909fa6761c4e1776ed6c51bbd5227465","tid":2155760,"uid":263213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:29:00.000Z","msg":"從來都冇一個正常嘅教育會叫人依附極權<br />\n所以藍絲讀屎片大嘅"},{"pid":"044e1e3fdef98f1955570dcc54a6d9ab7a19bde0","tid":2155760,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"853923a4b655969acd5d34b3837e8c679e3dfec5","tid":2155760,"uid":32859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:27:27.000Z","msg":"睇到鄧同強就覺得係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T04:31:28.000Z","msg":"仲有謝振中個振字<br />\n似乎可以負負得正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a946137c0a91ad18f2792a702aa41cee1acefc","tid":2155760,"uid":187232,"like":0